---
// The /signs page has been merged into /roadcode as the 「交通標誌・原圖庫」
// section. This stub remains so old bookmarks and deep-links continue to
// resolve — it ships a meta-refresh plus a manual link for non-JS / slow
// clients, and is otherwise cheap (no catalog import, no grid render).
const target = "/roadcode#catalog-標誌圖鑑";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>交通標誌・的士筆試</title>
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content={`0; url=${target}`} />
    <link rel="canonical" href={target} />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang TC", sans-serif; padding: 48px 24px; color: #333; }
      a { color: #c83232; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>交通標誌・原圖庫已併入<a href={target}>道路守則頁面</a>。</p>
    <p><small>若瀏覽器未能自動跳轉，請按上方連結。</small></p>
    <script define:vars={{ target }}>
      // Belt-and-suspenders: fire a client redirect in case meta-refresh is disabled.
      window.location.replace(target);
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
